KUSHONE abantu abangu-6 kwalimala abangu-50 engozini yebhasi namhlanje ekuseni emgwaqeni u-N8 ngaseBloemfontein, eFree State. &nbsp;Kubikwa ukuthi le ngozi yenzeke ngesikhathi ibhasi lingqubuzana neloli ebelimile ku-N8. Okhulumela abezimo eziphuthumayo i-ER24, uMnuz Russel Meiring, uthe bafice uhlangothi ololudwa lwebhasi luvulekile lonke, kanti ibhasi neloli besekuphaphalazele eceleni komgwaqo. &nbsp; Abezimo eziphuthumayo balekelele abantu abebelimele, ngeshwa sathola ukuthi abesifazane abangu-6 balimale kakhulu, bashonela endaweni yesigameko. Bekungekho ebesingakwenza. &nbsp;Uthe kulimale abantu abangu-50 kule ngozi. &nbsp; Oyedwa wabo kudingeke ukuthi aphuthunyiswe esibhedlela ngendiza, kuqhuba yena. &nbsp;Amaphoyisa abekhona endaweni yengozi ukuzophenya ngembangela yayo.